General installation instructions:

 0.  Install Apache, Python, MySQL, and Gnuplot.   These should 
     all be 'standard components' for modern linux systems.
 
 1. Install epics base

 2. Install python extensions.

 2. Set up MySQL permissions.

 3. Install Web scripts, configure Apache mod_python.

 4. Add some PVs to be collected.

 5. Start data collection.

 6. View / Modify web pages

 7. Set up cron scripts to manage databases

 8. Continue to add PVs and/or modify web pages

 
 
